    19	## Tenant-side shared state (per-profile-collision-risk)
    20	| Resource | Shared by N profiles? | Collision risk | Isolation strategy |
    21	|----------|-----------------------|----------------|--------------------|
    22	| Gateway `Lab GW Rocky` | yes | low (read-mostly) | none needed |
    23	| Admin Commander session | yes (admin login is global) | HIGH if shared `~/.keeper/` | per-profile `KEEPER_CONFIG=/path/to/profile-N/.keeper-config.json` env var |
    24	| testuser session | per-profile by definition | none | already isolated |
    25	| Shared folder | per-profile | none | already isolated |
    26	| KSM app | per-profile | none | already isolated |
    27	| Marker channel | per-profile | none | already isolated |
    28	| Audit alerts / SCIM endpoints | tenant-global | medium | optionally per-profile node |
    29	| Tenant write throttle | yes (Commander API rate limits) | medium | document N≤3 as default |
    30	
    31	## Process-side shared state
    32	| Resource | Risk | Mitigation |
    33	|----------|------|------------|
    34	| `keeper` CLI in subprocess | shared `~/.keeper/` config; race on `params.json` rewrite | each profile MUST set `KEEPER_CONFIG=<unique path>` (verify Commander honours; cite Commander source if available) |
    35	| pytest cache | benign | per-profile `--profile` token in artifact paths |
    36	| `/tmp/dsk-*` temp files | benign if PID-suffixed | smoke already PID-suffixes; confirm |
